# get_irida_sequence_run
# get IRIDA OAuth token for admin account and export as IRIDA_TOKEN
#
# examples:
#   get_irida_sequence_run
#   get_irida_sequence_run 42
#
# WARNING: this function requires an admin token to get data, 
# otherwise, you will get an empty json response.
# use get_irida_token_admin to get the admin account.
